{"tid":1119050,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"趙敏撐起新倚天","createTime":"2019-04-21T16:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T14:42:39.000Z","uid":241636,"like":42,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"379c465bb60c5c9b506edc28aca9389106e3c7cd","tid":1119050,"uid":241636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T16:29:44.000Z","msg":"一如其他金庸電視劇，新倚天屠龍記一定會被人與舊版本比較。<br />\n新倚天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n劇情推進太慢<br />\n張無忌演技一般（但算合格）<br />\n角色小瑕疵(周海湄不太適合滅絕師太的形象)<br />\n<br />\n新倚天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n演員強陣容強盛(樊少皇、周海媚)<br />\n趙敏演技一流，合符原作郡主機智多謀，心思敏捷，同時敢愛敢恨的蒙古女子性格。劇中小表情都幾多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HyEQ3hL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHyEQ3hL.png&h=6c1f2c4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW想問下有幾個男人頂得住趙敏呢個表情<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zdw75wv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZdw75wv.gif&h=26beddcd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zVb75wx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzVb75wx.gif&h=0dce75af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S<br />\n現實又有幾多個楊逍咁樣的痴情種<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUa1qxN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUa1qxN.png&h=e162f642&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca25881d730b3402ca85c3072aae9ebfb6f1ce5d","tid":1119050,"uid":152712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T13:51:00.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2b29cad3b4b6c343f74afba3f5c6285230f46c",